{"tid":2477669,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲廣播公司：上海公安局數據外洩　揭5000外國人受中國監控","createTime":"2021-04-06T12:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T04:02:19.000Z","uid":261647,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7065446f35aeeca6b9a82079d2ccc2c92f517403","tid":2477669,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617270713_SB-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617270713_SB-1280w.png&h=1d1995ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/澳洲廣播公司：上海公安局數據外洩%E3%80%80揭5000外國人受監控-262399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%BB%A3%E6%92%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9%25E3%2580%2580%E6%8F%AD5000%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7-262399&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtT9kuezr8BQg8uGmIe3q97E%3D&h=5b27b0f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/澳洲廣播公司：上海公安局數據外洩%E3%80%80揭5000外國人受監控-262399</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617267612_pB-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617267612_pB-1280w.jpg&h=d7e6a721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲廣播公司報道，上海公安局數據外洩，揭有5,000名外國人受監控。(澳洲廣播公司網頁截圖)<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司(ABC)報道，中國上海市公安局一個安全數據庫去年底遭黑客入侵，發現超過110萬份公安局的文件及監控紀錄，包括逾5,000名外國人，當中至少有161名澳洲公民及150名英國公民；還有2.5萬名新疆維吾爾族人、政治異見者等，其中逾400人是未成年人士，最細只得5歲。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，黑客竊取相關資料後，轉交網絡安全公司Internet 2.0，Internet 2.0再轉交澳洲安全官員、ABC及少數國際媒體。資料庫存有數以萬計的公安局監視名單、線人報告、臉部及車輛識別相片、移民數據，包括2017年起到訪過上海的數千名外國人護照詳情及照片，當中不乏外國政府官員及商界領袖，包括前澳洲駐日本大使、國家評估情報分析機構辦公室主任Geoff Miller。<br />\n<br />\nGeoff Miller回應指，他曾與澳洲總理及部長多次到中國，相信因此成為中國當局關注對象。澳洲雜誌《媒體周刊》(Mediaweek)合夥人Janis Manning曾在上海逗留一天，Janis Manning對自己被納入數據庫感到難以理解，但指可能與她的工作會接觸到一些傳媒高層。<br />\n<br />\nInternet 2.0行政總裁Robert Potter指出，相信文件屬中國大規模監控系統的一部分，有助外界了解中國結合刑事調查與政治部門，追蹤異見人士的手法。"},{"pid":"8760b64239c30ab8180543fa4a0a2e04a7083bbb","tid":2477669,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2455a67220a81a1b61220dd5c6c43705ce247f","tid":2477669,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4593dd3c0b918a1713c2543c3d933110c1f05021","tid":2477669,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"上海都5000，北京起碼50萬"},{"pid":"5aecd9e66c52393aae7349af07e8782c2dd7caf5","tid":2477669,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"呢d沉得太快"},{"pid":"e3d5dbd07ccc2bea31c2f6c3681ce91a232e0f80","tid":2477669,"uid":162477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:35:41.000Z","msg":"冇五毛支持！"},{"pid":"4e16710715ff9e2b76a2cda1db4ca021de0d3b87","tid":2477669,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"鑊鑊都係澳洲爆先<br />\n真係急先鋒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd10d27cca061de80338363769aba29fcbe1422","tid":2477669,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a956ec72a344f324796abe6f4baa5869a575d68","tid":2477669,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"你唔係